{"tid":424422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖] 頭先食飯對面坐咗兩姊妹","createTime":"2017-10-04T16:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T17:04:39.000Z","uid":133611,"like":635,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"2112548455cf05a648c7da32b3676376ee2d045b","tid":424422,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的　頭先同屋企人去食飯　搭檯對面坐咗三母女<br />\n兩姊妹嘅對話幾有趣<br />\n<br />\n家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樣一般　無化妝　Hea　打扮　帶眼鏡<br />\n細妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾靚女　幾白　有化妝　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫咩食好呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    不如叫燒味啊　呢度啲燒味幾好食啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好啦，大時大節仲食燒味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    我上次食過啲燒腩真係OK　喎.........(細細聲講)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫嘢食啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    唔好啦，呀哥都未到，等埋佢先啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好肚餓呀，叫啲嘢食下啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    等埋佢啦，佢就到啦...<br />\n(家姐照叫)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我男朋友請啦今餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    唔好啦，佢係都要比錢先算啦，我地咁多人食唔係幾好㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次見緊係佢請啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    好貴姐....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你條仔呢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    佢要做完節先過到嚟，會遲少少呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中秋都遲到，咁唔尊重㗎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    咁人地都係中秋姐.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀媽，我呢度好「支力」，幫我按下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴線，要呀媽大庭廣眾幫你按摩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無所謂啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉我幫你喇<br />\n<br />\n我係身邊聽到真係覺得家姐性格好好多<br />\n但感覺男人都係會比呀妹嘅外表吸引先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a34bf022f14e2381104a59468b5a114e096f06a","tid":424422,"uid":19560,"like":543,"dislike":12,"score":531,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔信你<br />\n不過你開左個post，我滿心期望入到黎<br />\n一打開，屌，原來圖都冇幅<br />\n如果你有幅圖既，就算假既都好過冇<br />\n起碼我都知你條友仔係度吹水唔抹嘴，唔洗我郁手都有其他巴打問候伯母<br />\n點知家陣冇野證明到你講既野係岩<br />\n又冇野證明到你講既野係錯<br />\n就好似係街果D gay篤桃咁，同你講上帝存在<br />\n問佢點解存在，又話係因為你證明唔到佢唔存在<br />\n大佬呀，我已經好煩，唔好再同我講埋佛計（偈）<br />\n一句到尾，你而家都係冇圖<br />\n冇圖既你開個post做乜？<br />\n人地入到盞令伯友難做，點解要咁不孝？<br />\n不孝有三，無圖為大，而家我唔理你，話知你猴子偷圖，點都死幅圖出黎"},{"pid":"1675edb3173e425e7695feee538f80c4975fd070","tid":424422,"uid":19005,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5e05d50df9c7a402915149dd0a17632f6158f6","tid":424422,"uid":151245,"like":14,"dislike":47,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"做家姐多數性格都正啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87782d43671d980db2bae94ff9df5c2dca7cd32b","tid":424422,"uid":38934,"like":154,"dislike":3,"score":151,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:27:40.000Z","msg":"真係用icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d3dc189ea322b4bf6ea4669c4d24b43ff37089","tid":424422,"uid":49228,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"hea打扮嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5926d60